reviewText: I will say that my boys like the dancing dinosaurs. And the weird animation is kooky enough to hold their attention.  I do like these videos much better than little Pim which feel a lot more abrupt and harder to follow to me. That said, they didn't really learn Japanese so I can't really give it more than three stars.  And I only gave it three stars for the entertainment value.
So cute my toddler loves it
